<span class="subhead">Slash Makes Visit to Gibson Guitar Exhibit</span>

<br><br><IMG height=158 src="/images/ces_photos/Slash.jpg" width=110 align=right>With his trademark Gibson Les Paul, top hat and cigarette, iconic rock-n-roller Slash will make an exclusive visit to the Gibson Guitar Booth&nbsp;2 p.m. Wednesday, January 10. The former Guns N Roses guitarist and Velvet Revolver frontman will be available for press coverage and photos. Fans can also view Slash’s Gibson Signature model at the booth.<BR><BR><STRONG>Who:</STRONG> Slash from Guns N Roses and Velvet Revolver<BR><STRONG>Where:</STRONG>&nbsp; Gibson Guitar Booth,&nbsp;LVCC Central Plaza, CP-1<BR><STRONG>When:</STRONG> Wednesday, January 10, 2007 at 2pm<BR><STRONG>Why:</STRONG> Slash makes a visit to the most talked about booth at CES and the maker of his signature Gibson Les Paul guitar. <BR><BR>Slash is added to the long list of celebrity musicians who have hung out at the Gibson Guitar booth including ZZ Top’s Billy Gibbons, Billy Bob Thornton, Devon Allman and others.

